{"tid":1729102,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"原來14億人死就可以清洗人類的罪行","createTime":"2019-11-17T06:18:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-17T12:10:40.000Z","uid":149342,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6611b3e3dd6caec1c05250ced01b3927e91bb966","tid":1729102,"uid":149342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T06:18:43.000Z","msg":"大家都知道，耶穌死，清洗了人類的罪行。<br />\n原本中國14億人死，亦能清洗人類的罪，purify 人類心靈。<br />\n因為14億人一死，規模巨大，首先，直接心靈影響有兩種，一種係好爽爽，一種係好可憐，爽爽之人，心靈得到了滿足，負情緒一掃而空。覺得可憐之人，測忍之生油然而生，世界充滿愛。<br />\n14億人一死，報應之証，讓人反思己過，自然左心生罪念時自我改正。<br />\n最重要是14億人，一個蘑菇也沒有，人類總体罪惡，即時少了6成"},{"pid":"b95d10e3707e612890deefb9f3b02e2942e124a5","tid":1729102,"uid":303982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T07:05:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec2bb7373ba9131a2aa5488ab95d3ad48ec9a706","tid":1729102,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T11:51:35.000Z","msg":"蚑那徹底滅亡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8294e12eaaf633a1057ad8d31ee17722a70b0fb5","tid":1729102,"uid":78764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T12:09:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc0b30447ed4c1d65db0f7e0e1e287b3dc5e579c","tid":1729102,"uid":64290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T12:10:40.000Z","msg":"所以出現了黑死病"}]}